    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Keep Those Bugs Away From The Bomb》这款快节奏的弹幕射击冒险游戏中体验不计其数的武器、升级与解锁内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/69275a6c1bad1a70f88750e7cc6ca9be.poster.avif?t=1764680654\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/69275a6c1bad1a70f88750e7cc6ca9be.webm?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/69275a6c1bad1a70f88750e7cc6ca9be.mp4?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗不断袭来的凶恶敌人，解救幸存者，解锁可游玩角色，获取全新武器与技能以扩充自己的军械库，最重要的是，不要……让……那些虫子……接近……炸弹！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/33ecc7b02ca8026c10f535a087b65cd0.poster.avif?t=1764680654\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/33ecc7b02ca8026c10f535a087b65cd0.webm?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/33ecc7b02ca8026c10f535a087b65cd0.mp4?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KTBAFTB将带来愈发严峻的挑战与永无止境的游玩内容。解锁并使用分为四大类的数十种毁灭性武器：金属、火焰、电流以及核子。利用关卡中找到的各类强化，化身真正的子弹地狱使者，同时不要……让……那些虫子……接近……炸弹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/5bced2c657c90159750d2b7cad716f02.poster.avif?t=1764680654\" width=780 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/5bced2c657c90159750d2b7cad716f02.webm?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133500/extras/5bced2c657c90159750d2b7cad716f02.mp4?t=1764680654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁千奇百怪的可游玩角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用数十种技能与强化升级你的英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五花八门的自动武器将允许你在穿越关卡时尽情宣泄火力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不计其数的外星敌人拥有着各自不同的行为与攻击模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要让那些虫子接近炸弹</p></li></ul>",
